    <article class="post card">
      <h1 class="post-title">{{Craving}}</h1>
      <div class="post-meta">{{Nov 10, 2025}} · {{Poetry, Illustration}}</div>
      <img class="ornament" src="../assets/ornaments/divider.svg" alt="divider"/>
      <section class="content">
<p>Swelling under the skin,
a fever that never breaks.<p>
<p>It waits between breaths,
tasting the air as it aches.<p>
<p>Like water, it moves in waves,
collapsing onto caves.<p>
<p>Prickling like urchins,
recedes in hesitation and lurches.<p>
<p>Salt stings the throat as it swallows urges,
but the eyes dilate, filled with perversions.<p>
      </section>
      <p class="signature">—with love and gratitude, Mezziah</p>
